@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ayeoou(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (0.68 - (wp.sin(v1 + 0.19) * v1))
    v2 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.75 - v1 + 0.31)) - wp.sin(v1))
    tmp = 0.80
    v0 = v0
    v2 = wp.cos((v2 - 0.16))
    v1 = (wp.abs(wp.cos(tmp + 0.88)) * wp.cos((tmp + 0.72 - v2 + 0.34)))
    v2 = wp.exp(0.12)
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.abs(v0))
    data[tid] = v0
